column5: me and my buddy had an awsome day of fishing on saturday...  10 carp 6 smallmouth bass 5 walleye 16 pike  and 2 sunburns...lol
Nice one Mike...sounds like fun.  Man i cant wait to hit the lake oin Wednesday....thanks for posting.
WTG!That is quite a mixed bag.

thnx guys... it was my first time pike  fishing...  we were trying to find spring walleye spots and lucked into some pike... then i used my gps to find a couple more spots that looked similar and the rest is history...
Nice shootin!  the best sunblock is LOTZ of tattoos (not really but its a good excuse)  Cheers
